snippet.title: Best Ever Pumpkin Pie Recipe!!
snippet.description:
Best Ever Pumpkin Pie Recipe!!
Toegevoegd door Lifestyle vorig jaar
Looking for the perfect fall or Thanksgiving holiday pie? Look no further than our great Best Ever Pumpkin (or squash) pie recipe. Ingredients: 2 cups cooked squash (we should use E.D. Smith canned pumpkin) 3/4 cup dark brown sugar 1/2 tsp course salt 1/2 tsp ground ginger 1 tsp cinnamon 1/4 tsp nutmeg 3 eggs 1 1/4 cups milk 3/4 cup heavy cream Method: Combine squash, sugar, and spices. In a separate bowl slightly beat eggs add milk, the stir into squash mixture. Pour into un-baked pie shell. Bake at 400ยบ for 15-20 minutes, then lower oven temp to 325ยบ. Continue baking until custard has set. 35-40 minutes for shallow pies, 60 minutes for deep dish pie.
